# Netflix Power BI Dashboard

## Project Overview
This Power BI dashboard analyzes Netflix content data and provides insights into:
- Total Shows
- Ratings Distribution
- Genres Analysis
- Movies vs TV Shows
- Release Year Trends
- Country-wise Distribution

## Tools Used
- Power BI
- Excel
- Data Visualization

## Key Insights
- TV-MA is the most common rating.
- Movies dominate the content library.
- Content production increased after 2015.
